@node Overview
@chapter Overview

This package wraps the project's Python and shell build scripts, running them asynchronously via @samp{compile} so output appears in a compilation buffer with proper error highlighting. See @samp{PUBLISHING.md} in the Hugo repo for additional details.

The development repository is on @uref{https://github.com/benthamite/stafforini.el, GitHub}.

@node Workflows
@chapter Workflows

There are two tiers of commands: @strong{interactive export} for single-file edits during day-to-day work, and @strong{batch commands} for bulk operations. You rarely need both at once.

